# Coding Standards (Strict)

## PSR Compliance
- Must follow PSR-12 strictly.

## Naming Rules
- Class → PascalCase
- Method → camelCase
- Variable → camelCase
- Constant → UPPER_SNAKE_CASE

## Structure Rules
- One class per file
- No god classes (>300 lines not allowed)

## Code Quality
- No duplication (DRY enforced)
- Early return pattern preferred
- Avoid nested conditions (>3 levels forbidden)